(4, 113, 2, 'PlusPower', 'Attach PlusPower to your Active Pokémon. At the end of your turn, discard PlusPower. If this Pokémon''s attack does damage to the Defending Pokémon (after applying Weakness and Resistance), the attack does 10 more damage to the Defending Pokémon.'),
(4, 114, 2, 'Pokémon Center', 'Remove all damage counters from all of your own Pokémon with damage counters on them, then discard all Energy cards attached to those Pokémon.'),
