(5, 11, 2, 'Dark Magneton', '[C][C] Sonicboom : 20\r\nDon''t apply Weakness and Resistance for this attack. (Any other effects that would happen after applying Weakness and Resistance still happen.)\r\n\r\n[L][L] Magnetic Lines : 30\r\nIf the Defending Pokémon has any basic Energy cards attached to it, choose 1 of them. If your opponent have any Benched Pokémon, choose 1 of them and attach that Energy card to it.'),
